    "The process of the parameter fine-tuning is follows.",
    "All the sentence similarities {x i } N i=1 in a corpus are computed by AQE, where N represents the number of sentence pair in the corpus.",
    "The variance between the calculated value x i and the annotated value y i dictates whether it is essential to reevaluate x i using dimension reduction models.",
    "If the computed score of the sentence pair conforms to Eqs.",
    "14 and 15, it is deemed a valid outcome."
